As used in KRS 212.780 to 212.794 the following definitions shall apply:
"Board" means independent district board of health as created in KRS 212.780 to 212.794;
"Cabinet" means Cabinet for Health and Family Services;
"County board of health" means a local board of health as defined by KRS 212.640 or 212.020;
"Department" means independent district department of health created in KRS 212.780 to 212.794;
"Director" means the district director of health;
"District board of health" means the district board of health as established pursuant to KRS 212.810 to 212.930;
"District department of health" means the district department of health as established pursuant to KRS 212.810 to 212.930;
"Independent district board of health" means the independent district board of health as created in KRS 212.780 to 212.794;
"Judge/executive" means the county judge/executive of any county fiscal court as defined in KRS 67.700 to 67.710; and
"Metropolitan statistical area" (MSA) means metropolitan statistical area as defined by the United States Bureau of the Census, United States Department of Commerce.
